yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Amɨn Dakon Monji da tepmɨ madepsi pakdɨsak. Aŋakwan kɨla amɨn, ae mukwa sogok amɨn dakon amɨn madep kabɨ, ae gen teban yoyɨŋdet amɨn gat da manji ɨmɨŋek aŋakba kɨmotdɨsak. Kɨmagek gɨldat kapbɨ aŋakwan kɨmoron da pɨdokdɨsak."
Yawe, gak da uwalgo gen tebai yoyɨŋaki mɨrɨm madep da yaŋ butjapgo da pɨsoŋban dukwan dukwan kwaŋ. Gak da butjapgo da tap ɨdap aban kɨbɨdaŋ mudoŋ, aŋakwan mɨktɨm aŋteban ak dakon yo nomansi teŋteŋoŋ.
Mani on olapgo uŋun kɨmakgɨt da aeni abɨdosok, do kɨsɨk kɨsɨk aŋek butnin paŋteban asak.' "
Gak jomjom aŋek Yawe da aŋpulugosak do jomjom abi. Tebaisi agek butgo dɨma jɨk toni. Yawe da aŋpulugosak do jomjom aŋek egɨpbi.
Aŋek Piŋkop da Amɨn Kɨla Asak uŋun dakon gen yaŋ teŋteŋoni ae sot amɨn paŋmɨlɨp ani do yabekgɨt.
Aŋakwa uŋun amɨn kɨsisi Telagɨ Wup da burɨkon pɨgɨ tugaŋba gen mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ yaŋek gen yawit.
Nak asisi dayɨsat, ji nak dɨma nandaŋek nak dɨma nandaŋakwa bɨsap madepmon 'On amɨn Amɨn Tagɨ da manon abɨsak, uŋun Piŋkop da gɨsamɨgakwan abɨsak' yaŋ nak do yoni uŋun bɨsapmon nandakdaŋ."
Nido amɨn kɨmakbi yokwi da kɨsiron dɨma ekwaŋ.
Mani pi amɨn kɨnda dakon yutni soŋban pasɨljak kaŋ, pi morapni pasɨl mudokdaŋ. Pi amɨn iyɨ dɨma pasɨljak, mani amɨn kɨnda kɨndapmon da pulugaŋ kɨsak uŋun yombem egɨpdɨsak.
Nak da mɨktɨm yɨpbo tap madep Mediterenian da arɨpmon kɨŋek pakbi madep Yupretis da arɨpmon kɨŋ mudokdaŋ.
Yesu Telagɨ Yut Madep dakon nagal yɨpmaŋek waŋga kɨŋakwan paŋdetni kɨnda da yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Yoyɨŋdet, pɨndat, on tɨp madep tagɨsi gat, ae yut madep tagɨsi gat pɨndat!"
Nandani, namɨn da mibɨltok amɨn asak? Jap noknok tamokon yɨkdak amɨn, bo pi amɨn jap pɨlɨk paŋopmaŋdak? Mibɨltok amɨn uŋun dagɨn jap nosok. Mani nak oman amɨnji da tɨlak jikon egɨsat.
Jerusalem kokup papmon egɨpgwit amɨn kɨsi da yo uŋun dakon mibɨlɨ nandawit. Do uŋun mɨktɨm tɨm amɨn da iyɨ da genon da Akaldama yaŋ yoŋ. Akaldama uŋun dakon mibɨlɨ uŋun Yawi Mɨktɨm.
Yesu da yaŋ pɨndagek burɨ yokwi taŋban paŋdetni yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Mɨŋat monjɨyo yopba nagon apgut. Dɨma kɨrɨŋɨk yomni. Piŋkop da Amɨn Kɨla Asak uŋun amɨn mɨŋat monjɨyo da tɨlagon ekwaŋ uŋuden amɨn dakon.
Yaŋdo, not kabɨno, ji butji yaworɨ taŋakwa jɨgɨ guramɨgek Amɨn Tagɨ aeni apjak uŋun do jomjom ani. Dɨsi nandaŋ, pi ami uŋun pigaga jap bamɨ tagɨsi paŋ pigagani do jomjom asak. Uŋun butni yaworɨ taŋakwan sɨkak gat ae gɨldat gat da pini bamot aŋakwa don jap bamɨ pasak do jomjom asak.
Aŋakwa Sol niaŋ aŋatdaŋ dakon geni nandaŋek kɨmakgɨt. Yaŋ aŋakwan Juda amɨn da Sol aŋakba kɨmotjak do gɨldarɨ ae kalbiyo kɨsi kokup pap dakon yoma domon kɨla aŋek kaŋ egɨpgwit.
Piŋkop, monjɨ gɨmoŋɨ egɨpgum dakon yokwino do saŋbeŋek dɨma nandaki. Gak Piŋkop but dasi galak taŋ yomɨŋek tagɨsi egɨsal. Nandaŋ namɨŋek bupmɨ nandaŋ nabi.
Paŋmuwukbi uŋun Kristo dakon gɨptɨm. Kristo uŋun yo morap kɨsikon egek yo morap kɨsi tugaŋ mudagɨt.
Nak mayagɨ dɨma pakeŋ, do gengo do kɨla amɨn madep madepmon yaŋ teŋteŋokdɨsat.
Abraham Piŋkop da yo morap ak do yaŋ teban tok agɨt uŋun niaŋ aŋek aŋmudosak uŋun dɨma nandagɨt. Mani nandaŋ gadatni uŋun bamɨ noman tokdaŋ yaŋ nandaŋ gadat agɨt. Aŋek Piŋkop da yaŋ yagɨt: "Gak dakon gwakgo morapmɨsi da ɨreŋ taŋ ani." Do uŋun da arɨpmon 'amɨn kabɨ morapmɨ dakon kɨla amɨn madep dagagɨt.'
Sipsip da yaŋ kɨmakbi kokupmon pɨgɨni do Piŋkop da kɨlɨ manjɨgɨt. Kɨmot da kɨla amɨni egɨpdɨsak. Yutni tagɨsi ae gɨptɨmni wagɨlsi mɨktagɨlek kɨmakbi kokupmon pɨgɨni bɨsapmon amɨn kɨlegɨ da uŋun noman taŋ yomgwit do kɨsɨk kɨsɨk ani.
Mɨktɨm morap dakon kɨla amɨn madepni emat ak do tagap toŋ. Uŋun muwugek Amɨn Tagɨ gat ae Kristo iyɨ paŋpulugosak do manjɨgɨt amɨni gat pabɨŋ yop do muwukgaŋ." '
Nak nandɨsat, Dat dakon gen da egɨp egɨp dagok dagogɨ mɨni nimɨsak yaŋ nandɨsat. Do gen morap yosot uŋun Dat da nayɨgɨt uŋun baŋgɨn yosot."
"Juda amɨn kɨsi morap da nak dakon mibɨlno pakyaŋsi nandaŋ namaŋ. Nak monɨŋɨsogon da dabɨno da binapmon egek don Jerusalem kɨgɨm uŋun nandaŋ namgwit.
Bɨsap kɨndakon Sekaraia dakon dɨwatni da kɨŋ mukwa sogok pi awit. Sekaraia yo kɨsi Piŋkop da dabɨlon mukwa sogok pi agɨt.
Yaŋ yaŋakwa amɨn dɨwarɨ da yawit, "Elaija abɨkdak." Ae dɨwarɨ da yawit, "Kombɨ amɨn kalɨpmɨ kɨnda da kɨmoron da pɨdagɨt."
Yawe, amɨn tagɨ, amɨn nin bɨsap pɨsɨpmɨsok ekwamaŋ do nandaŋ nibi. Gak da nin wasagɨl, mani nin kɨsisi kɨmak mudaŋek tasɨk tomaŋ.
Ae Piŋkop dakon kokup pap madep kagɨm, uŋun Jerusalem kalugɨ, uŋun kagɨm. Uŋun kaŋapbo Kwen Kokup da Piŋkop gat pɨŋban pɨgɨt. Mɨŋat kɨnda da amɨn do mɨŋat pak do asak uŋun da tɨlɨmni tagɨsi paŋek amɨni pak do asak uŋun da tɨlak kɨlɨ paŋtɨlɨmni tagɨsi paŋnoman agɨt.
"Ji kɨni. Nak da ji sipsip monɨŋ joŋ pɨŋan da bɨkbɨgon yaŋ yabekdat.
Pol uŋun yutnon wɨŋakwan Juda amɨn Jerusalem egɨpgwit uŋun da Pestus aŋgwasɨŋek abɨŋ yaŋ ɨmɨŋek gen yaŋ ɨmgwit. Yaŋ yaŋek Pestus do yo yokwisi morapmɨsi agɨt dakon mibɨlɨ yaŋ ɨmgwit, mani gen uŋun bamɨsi yaŋ arɨpmɨ dɨma yolɨgwit.
Jikon da dɨwarɨ nak dɨma opbeŋ yaŋ nandaŋek kwen wɨgɨk aŋ.
Uŋun da yokwi mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ aŋ gamgut, bo ae goman gagon tosok kaŋ, uŋun amɨn dakon man kulabɨk aŋek nak dakon man uŋun gagon mandaki.
Yawe da mɨŋat amɨnyo paŋpulugaŋban aŋpak kɨlegɨkon kɨkdaŋ, aŋakwan uŋun da kositni aŋnoman asak.
Yaŋ yaŋba yoyɨgɨt, "Gen morap on dakon mibɨlɨ ji nandaŋ?" Yaŋban iyɨwit, "Asi nandaŋ."
Amɨn yokwi gat ae gulusuŋ aŋ amɨn gat kɨsi dɨma abɨŋ nepbi. Gen galagɨ yoŋ amɨn gat dɨma abɨŋ nepbi, mani nandak nandak yokwi butnikon tugawit da toŋ uŋun gat dɨma abɨŋ nepbi.
Yaŋ yaŋakwa Juda amɨn dɨwarɨ kɨsi da Tetulus dakon gen aŋpulugaŋek Pol gulusuŋ agɨt yaŋ yaŋek yawit, "Gen morap uŋun bamɨsi yoŋ."
Uŋun amɨn bamot kɨŋ altaŋ yomgumal, do Piŋkop da Telagɨ Wup yomjak do bɨsit pi awit, nido Telagɨ Wup dɨma uŋun kabɨkon pɨgɨt. Yesu da manon gɨn telagɨ pakbi sowit.
Dewit yo kɨsi da uŋun do yaŋ yagɨt: "Jap madep ak do muwutni bɨsapmon paron yokwalni, ae gapmagwan maŋek yokwalni, ae kandapni tɨp baŋ tɨdaŋba kobogɨ yokwisi tɨmɨtneŋ do bɨsap madepsi yomjak.
Ji kombɨ amɨn dakon babɨkni kabɨ ekwaŋ. Ae Piŋkop da saŋbek saŋbek agɨt bɨsapmon babɨkji gat yaŋ teban tok aŋ yomgut bɨsapmon yo tagɨ dam do yaŋ teban tok aŋ damgut. Piŋkop da Abraham yaŋ iyɨgɨt: 'Gak dakon babɨkgo do aŋek mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ amɨn morap yo tagɨsi aŋ yomdɨsat.'
Yaŋ yaŋba mukwa sogok amɨn dakon amɨn madep kabɨ gat ae gen teban yoyɨŋdet amɨn gat uŋun kɨsi yaŋba yokwi tok aŋek notni yoyɨŋ yoyɨŋ aŋek yaŋ yawit, "Uŋun da amɨn dɨwarɨ paŋpulugagɨt, mani iyɨ aŋpulugok do aŋtɨdok asak.
Mani nin nandamaŋ, amɨn kɨnda Moses dakon gen teban guramɨkdak uŋun do aŋek Piŋkop da amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ dɨma iyɨsak. Amɨn kɨnda Yesu Kristo nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmɨsak uŋuden amɨn do Piŋkop da amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ iyɨsak. Nin Yesu Kristo nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmamaŋ. Nido nin yaŋsi nandamaŋ, uŋun kosiron dagɨn Piŋkop da amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ niyɨsak, gen teban yolyol kosiron da dɨma. Nido, amɨn kɨnda gen teban guramɨgek Piŋkop da amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ arɨpmɨ dɨmasi iyɨsak.
Kokup pap morap tawit uŋudon agek yabekbi kabɨ gat ae kɨla amɨn gat Jerusalem kokup papmon egɨpgwit uŋun da gen kɨlɨ yaŋ aŋteban awit uŋun paŋmuwukbi yoyɨŋ mudawit. Gen uŋun yoyɨŋ mudaŋek guramɨtni do yoyɨwit.
Ae kɨla amɨn madep yɨtyɨt tamokon da amɨn kɨnda da madepsi yaŋ tɨdaŋek yaŋ yagɨt, "Nandani, Piŋkop dakon yut abɨsok amɨn gat egɨsak. Uŋun amɨn kabɨ da binapmon egakwan uŋun amɨn kabɨ iyɨ dakon mɨŋat amɨn kabɨ egɨpdaŋ. Asi, Piŋkop iyɨ uŋun amɨn kabɨ gat egek Piŋkopni egɨpdɨsak.
Yaŋban mɨŋat da yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Amɨn tagɨ, kɨnda mɨni." Yaŋ yaŋban Yesu da iyɨgɨt, "Nakyo kɨsi gen pikon dɨma gepbeŋ. Gak kɨŋek don yokwi saŋbeŋek dɨma aki."
Piŋkop da Amɨn Kɨla Asak dakon gen yaŋ teŋteŋaŋek Amɨn Tagɨ Yesu Kristo dakon gen do yoyɨŋ teŋteŋagɨt. Uŋun pasol pasolɨ mɨni yaŋ teŋteŋaŋakwan amɨn da dɨma kɨrɨŋɨk ɨmgwit.
Mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ ekwaŋon amɨn Piŋkop do pasal ɨmɨŋek aŋpak kɨlegɨ aŋ amɨn uŋun but dasi galak taŋ yomɨsak.
Yaŋ aŋakwan kombɨ amɨn kɨnda da kalɨpsigwan gen yaŋ yagɨt uŋun bamɨ noman tagɨt. Gen uŋun yaŋ yagɨt: "Nak da tɨlak gen dayɨko gen ŋwakŋwarɨ dayɨkeŋ. Yo kalɨpsigwan noman tawit da noman tawit bɨsapmon da wɨŋ abɨsok ekwamaŋ uŋun do yokdɨsat."
Mani gak gaga bɨsapmɨ bɨsapmɨ egɨp egɨp tagɨsi egɨpbi. Gak jɨgɨ tepmɨyo pakdɨsal. Gak mɨŋat amɨnyo Gen Bin Tagɨsi yaŋ teŋteŋok pi abi. Gak mɨŋat amɨnyo paŋpulugok pi abi, pi uŋun aŋ kɨmokgi.
"Ae amɨn kɨnda mibɨltok abɨŋ altagɨt uŋun da yaŋ yagɨt, 'Amɨn tagɨ, nak gol moneŋ tabɨlgo uŋun naŋ moneŋ ɨlɨt pi abo tabɨl 5 kabɨ noman tawit.'
Aŋakwan gɨkwem kagagwan da gen kɨnda yaŋ noman tagɨt: "Uŋun Monjɨno, nak da pini asak do manjɨgɨm. Ji geni nandani."
Yesu da kɨmoron da pɨdaŋek paŋdetni altaŋ yomgut uŋun kosirɨ kapbɨ agɨt.
Gen teban papia da yo tagɨsi don noman tokdaŋ dakon wupmɨ baŋgɨn pɨndakgamaŋ, mani uŋun dakon mibɨlɨ dɨma nolɨsak. Gen teban da bɨlagɨ bɨlagɨ mukwa kaloŋ kaloŋ naŋ gɨn mukwa soni do yosok, do nin nandamaŋ, gen teban da amɨn muwut muwut yutnon muwut muwut yutnon muwutni uŋun arɨpmɨ dɨma paŋmɨlɨp agagɨ. Gen teban da arɨpmɨ dɨma paŋmɨlɨp agagɨ.
Sadyusi amɨn dɨwarɨ da Yesukon apgwit. Sadyusi amɨn kabɨ uŋun amɨn kabɨ da amɨn kɨmakbi arɨpmɨ dɨma pɨdoni yaŋ nandaŋ.
Wɨsa dagaŋakwan paŋdetni yaŋ yoban opba paŋdetni 12 kabɨ manjɨgɨt. Yaŋ manjɨŋek yabekbi kabɨ do yaŋ yoyɨgɨt,
Yaŋdo, not kabɨ, nin oman mɨŋat dakon monjini dɨma. Nin mɨŋat ɨsal egɨsak dakon monjini ekwamaŋ.
Nak pɨlak pɨlak uŋun os da emat do tagap toŋ uŋun yombem pɨndakgɨm. Busuŋɨkon pelɨt gol baŋ wasaŋbi yombem toŋ. Ae tomno dabɨlni uŋun amɨn dakon yombem.
Nak Saimon Pita, nak Yesu Kristo dakon oman monjɨ ae yabekbini, ae Piŋkopnin ae Yokwikon Baŋ Tɨmɨt Tɨmɨt Amɨnin. Gen on mɨŋat amɨnyo nandaŋ gadat wagɨl tagɨsisi abɨdawit ji do mandɨsat. Yesu Kristo da aŋpak kɨlegɨsi agɨt do aŋek nandaŋ gadatji nin da nandaŋ gadat agɨmaŋ uŋudeŋ gɨn noman taŋ damgut.
Yaŋ aŋek ɨmal yutni Silon yɨpmaŋek kɨgɨt. Uŋun yutnon amɨn da binapmon egɨpgut.
Amɨn Tagɨ da saŋbeŋek yaŋ yagɨt, "Ji gen kokwin kɨla amɨn yokwi on da yosok uŋun nandani.
Pita yaŋ yaŋakwan muwut muwut yutnon amɨn gen kɨnda dɨma yaŋek tayaŋgok egek Banabas gat Pol gat dakon gen do mɨrak pakyaŋsi yopgwit. Yaŋ aŋek Piŋkop da paŋpulugaŋakwan wasok tapmɨmɨ toŋ Piŋkop da Amɨn Ŋwakŋwarɨ Kabɨkon agɨt uŋun dakon geni yaŋ teŋteŋaŋ yomgwit.
Ae Gen Bin Tagɨsi dayɨgɨm uŋun tebaisi abɨdoni kaŋ, Piŋkop da ji uŋun Gen Bin Tagɨsi do aŋek yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨtdɨsak. Yaŋ ani kaŋ, nandaŋ gadatji ɨsal dogɨn dɨma awit.
Amɨn kɨnda Piŋkop dakon mɨŋat amɨnyo dɨwarɨ paŋpulugosak dakon tapmɨm taŋ ɨmɨsak kaŋ, uŋun amɨn paŋpulugosak dakon pi aŋ kɨmotjak. Ae amɨn kɨnda yoyɨŋdet pi agak dakon tapmɨm taŋ ɨmɨsak kaŋ, uŋun yoyɨŋdet pi aŋ kɨmotjak.
Yaŋban Yesu da yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Amɨn kɨnda kɨsit kandapmɨyo abɨdaŋek yɨk nandarɨ mɨni kwen yo kɨsi pɨndakdak uŋun amɨn Piŋkop da Amɨn Kɨla Asak da kagagwan dɨma egɨsak."
Yaŋ aŋek Amɨn Tagɨ dakon mɨŋat amɨn kabɨni dakon aŋpak baŋ tagɨ yolni. Aŋakwa aŋpakji do but dasi galak taŋ damjak. Aŋek pi tagɨsi mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ morapmɨ akdaŋ. Aŋek Piŋkop nandaŋ ɨmdaŋakwa nandak nandakji uŋun toktogɨsi paptaŋ madepsi akdɨsak.
Gɨldarɨ gɨldarɨ mɨktɨmninon amɨn yokwi paŋupbal akdɨsat. Yokwi aŋ amɨn wɨrɨrɨkgo Yawe dakon kokup papmon saŋbeŋek dɨma egɨpni.
Dat da Monji but dasi galak taŋ ɨmɨŋek yo morap kɨla asak do kɨla agɨt.
Gɨkwem kagagwan yɨkgɨt amɨn uŋun sɨbani abɨdaŋek kɨŋ mɨktɨmon maŋek jap bamɨ tagɨsi mandaŋ dagagɨt.
Gak da mano madepsi aŋpapdɨsal. Aŋek butno aego aŋteban akdɨsal.
Piŋkop gen papia da Isip dakon kɨla amɨn madep do yaŋ yosok: "Nak da tapmɨm madepno gak do aŋek yaŋ aŋenokgo kɨla amɨn madep dagagɨl. Ae mɨktɨm morap kɨsikon man madepno do yaŋ teŋteŋok ani do aŋek man madepno mɨktɨm morap kɨsikon yaŋ teŋteŋoni do aŋek yaŋ dagagɨm."
Amɨn yokwi, ji tuŋon amɨn emarɨ toŋ yombem. Ji niaŋon da gen tagɨ yoni? Amɨn da nandak nandak mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ butnikon da toŋ uŋun baŋ yoŋ.
nido ae saŋbeŋek dɨma kɨmotdaŋ. Uŋun aŋelo yombem da ekwaŋ. Piŋkop da kɨmoron baŋ paban pɨdagɨt, do monjɨ gwayonisi ekwaŋ.
Do kɨmoron da pɨdoni bɨsap madepmon amɨn 7 kabɨkon namɨn dakon mɨŋatni asak? Kɨsi morap da pawit."
Asi, sipsip ae bulmakau gat ae bɨt kɨlap morap koron ekwaŋ,
Demitius uŋun amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ nandaŋ ɨmaŋ. Ae Piŋkop dakon gen bamɨ kɨsi uŋun amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ nandaŋ ɨmaŋ. Ae nakyo kɨsi uŋun amɨn kɨlegɨ yaŋ nandaŋ ɨmɨsat. Nak dakon gen uŋun bamɨsi yosot yaŋ nandɨsal.
Amɨn da aŋpak tagɨsi niaŋsi aŋdamni do nandaŋ, uŋun aŋpak amɨn do aŋyomni.
Amɨn uŋun kaŋek yo uŋun kagɨt uŋun do yaŋ teŋteŋok asak. Gen uŋun yaŋ teŋteŋok asak uŋun bamɨsi yosok. Iyɨ nandɨsak, do nandaŋ gadani.
Mɨŋat busuŋni dɨma wɨtjɨŋdak kaŋ, busuŋ daŋgwani pɨsɨpmɨsok dɨ mandaŋ mudosak. Ae busuŋ daŋgwani pɨsɨpmɨsok dɨma mandak do bo ae wagɨl kɨsisi wɨrɨrɨt do nandaŋ kaŋ, busuŋni wɨtjɨsak dosi nandɨsat.
Er uŋun Josua dakon monji. Josua uŋun Eliesa dakon monji. Eliesa uŋun Jorim dakon monji. Jorim uŋun Matat dakon monji. Matat uŋun Liwai dakon monji.
Nak asisi gayɨsat, gak dam tebanon sigɨn egaki wɨgɨ moneŋ niaŋ yopbi do gayɨni uŋun kɨsisi yopmaŋek don waŋga kɨkdɨsal."
Yoni mɨni amɨn ji gat bɨsapmɨ bɨsapmɨ egɨpdaŋ, mani nak ji gat bɨsapmɨ bɨsapmɨ dɨma egɨpdamaŋ."
Dat da yo morap agɨt uŋun do nandaŋek ŋwakbeŋ aŋ ɨmɨsat.
Ae busuŋ 7 kabɨ uŋun kɨla amɨn madep 7 kabɨ dakon tɨlak asak. 5 kabɨ uŋun kɨlɨ tasɨk tawit, ae kɨnda abɨsok egɨsak, ae kɨnda uŋun kɨla amɨn madep dɨma dagaŋbi. Uŋun kɨlɨ noman tosak bɨsap pɨsɨpmɨsok gɨn egɨpdɨsak.
Piŋkop, aŋpak yokwini aŋ, do kobogɨ yokwisi aŋ yobi. Butjap nandaŋ yomɨŋek pabɨŋ yopbi.
Yaŋba Yesu da yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Ji kɨŋ joŋ kɨlap yokwisi uŋun yaŋ iyɨni, 'Nandani, nak abɨsok koŋ yoldaŋ, ae aŋwa sot amɨn paŋmɨlɨp akdɨsat. Ae gɨldat kapbɨ egek pini aŋ mudokeŋ.'
Yokwi pakpak amɨn do yo yokwisi aŋ yobi bɨsapmon kɨmot dɨma abɨdoki. Amɨn dapdap amɨn gat kɨsi dɨma nɨkba kɨmokgeŋ.
Pailat da gen uŋun nandaŋek Yesu abɨdaŋ ɨlɨkban waŋga pɨgɨgɨmal. Pɨgakwan gen kokwin amɨn madep yɨtyɨt tamo tɨmon yɨkgɨt. Kokup uŋun kokup kɨnda mani Puluga Tɨp, ae Ibru genon da Gebata yaŋ yoŋ.
"Nin ɨlɨkba pɨgɨk garaŋɨ pudaŋkwi kon ɨmal dɨwat kalugɨ pakbikon dɨma sugaŋbi kɨnda naŋ dɨma bupmaŋgamaŋ. Yaŋ kaŋ, pakbikon sugono ɨmal dɨwat uŋun da garaŋɨ ɨlɨkban pudaŋ kɨ madepsi akdɨsak. Aŋakwan ɨmal dɨwat kalugɨ uŋun da garaŋɨ ɨlɨkban pudaŋ kɨ madepsi akdɨsak.
"Kɨla Amɨn Madep uŋun da amɨn gwandeŋ tetgɨn do yaŋ yoyɨsak, 'Amɨn pasɨldaŋ amɨn, ji nepmaŋ degek kɨŋ kɨndap tebanon kɨni. Kɨndap uŋun Sunduk gat ae aŋelo kabɨni gat do kɨlɨ aŋnoman abi uŋudon kɨni.
Do uŋun bɨsapmon gak paret tagɨsi ae kɨlegɨsi gat ae paret kɨndap da soŋban wagɨl soŋ mudoni uŋun do galagɨsi nandakdɨsal. Aŋek gak da altakon bulmakau wɨli baŋ mukwa sokdamaŋ.
"Amɨn Tagɨ Tapmɨm Ami, gak kaloŋ dagɨn kwensi egɨsal. Gak da yo morap wasagɨl. Gak da gaga dakon galaktok yo morap wasagɨl da noman tawit, ae abɨsok yo morap toŋ gɨn. Do amɨn morap kɨsi da gak do tagɨsi nandaŋek kɨsɨk kɨsɨk aŋek mango awɨgɨni."
Kaŋek uŋun yut dakon ami yaŋ iyɨnjil, 'Yoyɨŋdetnit da yosok, "Nak gat paŋdetnoni gat da Yapyap Bɨlak dakon jap noneŋ dakon yut burɨ dukwan tosok?" '
Mɨŋat bamorɨ da plaua wasaŋek yɨgakwal kɨnda yapmaŋek kɨnda abɨdokdɨsak."
Piŋkop dakon mɨŋat amɨn kabɨni, ji Piŋkop but dasi galak taŋ ɨmni. Piŋkop yolgaŋ amɨn uŋun kɨlani tagɨsi asak, mani kwen wugɨk aŋ amɨn uŋun kobogɨ yokwisi yomɨsak.
Aŋek Piŋkop da uwalni kandap mibɨlgwani yopban pɨŋbisi egɨpni do jomjom asak.
Ji Piŋkop da mɨŋat amɨnyo kɨla aŋek uwalji da kɨsiron yopgut uŋun pabɨŋ yop do dɨma ani. Ji aŋpak kɨlegɨsi aŋakwa uŋun da pɨndatni aŋek yolni.
Yaŋban Pita da yagɨt, "Gak da gen uŋun yosol nak dɨma nandɨsat." Yaŋ yaŋakwan uŋudon gɨn pup gen yagɨt.
Piŋkop da pi morap asak uŋun kɨlegɨsi gɨn asak. Nin but kaloŋon da pi tagɨsi aneŋ do nandɨsak. Paŋmuwukbi Piŋkop gawak ɨm do muwutni bɨsapmon mɨŋat gen dɨma yoni, gen mapmɨt gɨn yoni. Piŋkop dakon paŋmuwukbi morap da yaŋ gɨn aŋ. Mɨŋat da mibɨltok amɨn dɨma egɨpni. Moses dakon gen teban yolek pɨŋbini egɨpni.
Nandaŋ namɨŋek bɨsitno nandaki. Yaŋ teban tok agɨl uŋun da arɨpmon nak yokwikon naŋ abɨdoki.
Yaŋ yaŋban Pestus da yaŋ yagɨt, "Kɨla amɨn madep Agripa ae amɨn morap nin gat akgamaŋ ji kɨsi da on amɨn kaŋba pɨndakgaŋ. Juda amɨn morap Jerusalem ae ɨdon ekwaŋ ae ɨdon ekwaŋ kɨsi da uŋun amɨn gen yaŋ ɨmɨŋek aŋakba kɨmotjak do madepsi yaŋ tɨdaŋ namgwit. Aŋek dɨma egɨpjak do aŋakba kɨmotjak.
Gak yaŋ dɨma aŋek wupgokon da Piŋkop ya yaŋ iyɨki. Aŋaki amɨn kɨnda da gen yosol uŋun dɨma nandɨsak kaŋ, niaŋon da gak da Piŋkop ya yaŋ iyɨŋek 'Uŋun asi' yaŋ gayɨsak? Uŋun arɨpmɨ dɨma, nido gen yosol uŋun dɨma nandɨsak.
Piŋkop, gak Piŋkop egɨp egɨpmɨ toŋ. Amɨn kɨbɨrɨ pakbi do tegɨ kɨbɨdoŋ da yaŋ nak gak do but dasi galak taŋ gamɨsat. Piŋkop, ni bɨsapmon gak do obɨŋek gawak gamneŋ?
Ji pɨlɨn tuk aŋpak aŋ amɨn gat not dɨma aŋek egɨpni. Aŋpak uŋuden da bamɨ tagɨ dɨma paŋalon aŋ. Aŋpak uŋuden yokwi yaŋ mɨŋat amɨnyo da yolɨni kaŋ tagɨsi.
Mɨŋat amɨn kabɨgo nin do aego nandaki. Kalɨpsigwan mɨŋat amɨn kabɨgo nin manjɨgɨl, nin yumaŋ naŋ nipgul da gaga dakon amɨn kabɨsi ekwamaŋ. Saion Kabap tɨlɨmgo kalɨp egɨpgul uŋun do nandaki.
Asa uŋun Jeosafat dakon datni. Jeosafat uŋun Jeoram dakon datni. Jeoram uŋun Usia dakon datni.
Nandak nandakji kulabɨk aŋ kɨmotni.
Amɨn kaloŋ kɨnda da amɨn morap kɨsi do aŋek kɨmotjak kaŋ, uŋun da tagɨ dɨma asak. Ae amɨn kaloŋ kɨnda da amɨn morap kɨsi do aŋek kɨmotjak kaŋ, uŋun da tagɨ dɨma asak."
Amɨn dɨwarɨ kɨndakon da nin yokwikon baŋ arɨpmɨ dɨma tɨmɨtjak. Piŋkop da amɨn kɨsi morap Yesu da manon nin yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨtjak do manjɨgɨt."
Abɨsok jap naŋ tugok aŋ amɨn, awa! Don jap do akdaŋ. Abɨsok jɨkgo yanjaŋ amɨn, awa! Abɨsok jɨkgo yanjaŋ amɨn, awa! Abɨsok kunam tagek pakbi dabɨl pakdaŋ.
Gaga da tapmɨmon Jekop gat Josep gat dakon babɨni kabɨ don altawit uŋun yokwikon baŋ mɨŋat amɨn kabɨgo yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨkgɨl.
"Yoyɨŋdet, Moses da yaŋ mandagɨt, 'Amɨn kɨnda monjɨ mɨni da kɨmotjak kaŋ, padɨge da mɨŋatni paŋakwan monjɨ paŋalasak.'
Ae don yaŋ yagɨt, "Nak gak dakon galaktok yol do abɨsat." Yaŋ yaŋek aŋpak kalɨpmɨ uŋun wɨrɨrɨkban kɨŋakwan aŋpak kalugɨ da iyɨ dakon tamo abɨdosok.
Kɨŋ 3 kilok aŋakwan Yesu da yaŋ tɨdaŋek yaŋ yagɨt, " Eli, Eli lama sabaktani?" Gen uŋun dakon mibɨlɨ yaŋ: "Piŋkopno, Piŋkopno, nido nepmaŋ dekdal?"
Uŋun tepmɨsi abɨŋ dandɨsak kaŋ, dɨpmɨn pak ɨŋtaŋ damjak.
Yawe da nak dakon Amɨn Tagɨ yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Gak abɨŋ nak da amɨnsi tet do yɨkbɨ don uwalgo kandap gɨbaŋgogwan yopbo gengo guramɨtni."
Mɨrɨm ae tap pakbi madepsi tamalɨkgwit, do gɨldat kɨnda do tap wakga dakon pi monjɨ da yɨk madep maba tap kagagwan pɨgɨwit.
Ae Aisaia yo kɨsi da gen tebaisi yaŋ yagɨt: "Amɨn nak dɨma nak wɨsɨwit amɨn da nak kɨlɨ nandawit. Amɨn nak do dɨma yaŋba nandawit amɨn da nak kɨlɨ nandaŋ namgwit."
Kaŋakwa kaŋakwa Pilip da amɨn morapmɨkon koŋ morapmɨ yol yomgut, koŋ uŋun madepsi yaŋ tɨdaŋek yaŋ tɨdaŋek yɨpmaŋ degek kɨŋ kɨŋ mudawit. Aŋakwa amɨn morapmɨ kɨdarɨ gɨreŋɨ ae kandapni yokwi taŋbi uŋun kɨlek tawit.
Yo kabɨni uŋun gol, ae silwa, ae tɨp kɨldani tagɨsi, ae kɨndɨrɨŋ yumaŋ nogɨ wukwisi, ae ɨmal kwakwagɨ tagɨsi, ae ɨmal gami mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ, ae ɨmal paŋkɨbɨt, ae kɨndap kɨbaŋɨ tagɨsi mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ, ae elepan dakon geni baŋ wasaŋbi, ae kɨndap yumaŋ nogɨ wukwisi baŋ wasaŋbi, ae bras, ae ain, ae tɨp kɨldani toŋ tagɨsi baŋ wasaŋbi.
"Uŋun dɨma abɨdoki, dɨma noni, yum kaŋaki gɨptɨmgo dɨma saŋbesak?"
Ae mɨktɨm uŋun yɨpmaŋ dekgwit uŋun dogɨn nandawit tam, tobɨl kɨkdaŋ.
Yaŋ yaŋban mɨŋat uŋun waŋga pɨgek meŋi yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Meŋi iyɨŋbɨ yo ninaŋ namjak?" Yaŋban meŋi da yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Jon Telagɨ Pakbi Sogok Amɨn uŋun dakon busuŋɨ gak do tagɨ gabeŋ."
Yesu da saŋbeŋek yaŋ yagɨt, "Ae gen kɨnda babɨk da abɨdawit uŋun ji kɨlɨ nandawit. Gen uŋun yaŋ: 'Ji amɨn dɨma dapba kɨmotni. Ae amɨn kɨnda da amɨn kɨnda aŋakban kɨmotjak kaŋ, uŋun amɨn gen pikon atjak.'
Pol da gen uŋun yaŋakwan Pestus da madepsi yaŋ tɨdaŋek yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Pol, gak ŋugɨgɨsi. Nandak nandakgo madepsi, ae nandak nandakgo madepsi da ŋugɨgɨ asak!"
Yaŋ yaŋek uŋun kalbi binap aban kɨla amɨn madep da amɨn bamot tɨmɨkban wudani sugaŋ sugaŋbal amɨn bamot gat gwakni gat kɨsi telagɨ pakbi sowit.
Mɨktɨm uŋun da ɨleŋon bɨt kabɨ madep jap naŋek egakwa koŋ uŋun Yesu da nandaŋ yoban bɨt da butgwan pɨgɨni do bɨsit tebai iyɨwit. Iyɨŋba nandaŋ yoban pɨgɨwit.
"Yaŋ yoyɨŋba yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, 'Ji kɨsi kɨŋ wain pinokon kɨŋ pi ani. Pi aŋapbo pini arɨpmɨ da arɨpmon tomni damdɨsat.'
Uŋun bɨsapmon Maria tepmɨsi Judia mɨktɨmon kokup pap kɨnda kabapmon tosok uŋudon kɨgɨt.
Yawe da kɨlago aŋakwan yo yokwisi da dɨma aŋupbal ani. Yawe da kɨlago akdɨsak.
Ae nak kombɨ gen yaŋ teŋteŋaŋek Piŋkop dakon nandak nandak pasɨlɨ morap kɨsi nandaŋ pɨsokeŋ, ae nandak nandak morap kɨsi tɨmɨkgom, ae nandaŋ gadatno tebaisi taŋakwan ɨleŋ oba ɨlɨk aŋaŋ kɨkeŋ kaŋ, mani amɨn do but dasi galaktaŋ yomyom aŋpak nagon dɨma tosak kaŋ, nak yo ɨsalɨ.
Nak amɨn Piŋkop yolgaŋ uŋun baŋ galak taŋ yomdɨsat. Uŋun amɨn dagɨn nak gat yutnokon egɨpneŋ. Ae aŋpak kɨlegɨsi aŋ amɨn dagok dagogɨ mɨni aŋ amɨn uŋun dagɨn nak dakon pi ani.
Yaŋ yaŋba Yesu da yoyɨgɨt, "Ji abɨŋ jap noni." Yaŋ yaŋban paŋdetni si pasalgwit. Aŋek "Gak namɨn?" yaŋ dɨma iyɨwit amɨn kɨnda da dɨma iyɨgɨt. Yaŋ nandaŋek kɨlɨ nandawit, uŋun Amɨn Tagɨ.
Pol gɨldat tagɨ yaŋ yoyɨŋek Piŋkop da aŋpulugaŋakwan Amɨn Ŋwakŋwarɨ Kabɨkon yo morap agɨt uŋun dakon geni yoyɨgɨt.
Amɨn kɨnda paŋkewal morapmon tebaisi agek jɨgɨ guramɨkdak, uŋun amɨn kɨsɨk kɨsɨk tagɨ asak. Aŋakwan paŋkewal morapmon tebai agek tebai atjak kaŋ, Piŋkop da egɨp egɨp dagok dagogɨ mɨni dakon tomni ɨmdɨsak. Tomni uŋun Piŋkop da amɨn morap iyɨ do but dasi galak taŋ ɨmaŋ amɨn do yom do kɨlɨ yaŋ teban tagɨt.
Nido, Piŋkop Wukwisi dakon gen do nandaba wɨgakwa geni abɨŋ yɨpgwit.
Egɨp egɨp uŋun noman altaŋban kagɨmaŋ. Nin uŋun do yaŋ teŋteŋok amaŋ. Egɨp egɨp dagok dagogɨ mɨni uŋun do yaŋ teŋteŋok amaŋ. Uŋun Dat gat kɨsi egɨpgut da noman altaŋban kagɨmaŋ.
Yaŋ yaŋba Yesu da yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Ji dɨsi gen emat dɨma aŋ.
Kap yaŋek aŋkɨsini. Tambarin tɨdaŋek gita tɨdaŋek aŋkɨsini.
Yaŋba Yesu da nap teban kɨrɨŋ naŋ wamaŋ kɨrɨŋ kɨnda wasaŋek amɨn uŋun yolban waŋga abɨgɨwit. Aŋek amɨn uŋun gat sipsip ae bulmakau gat kɨsi yolba waŋga abɨgɨwit. Yaŋ aŋek Telagɨ Yut Madep yɨpmaŋek kɨwit. Yaŋ aŋek moneŋ kulabɨk awit amɨn dakon moneŋni gat ae tamoni gat kɨsi tagalgɨt.
Gak jap noknok madep asal bɨsapmon, yoni mɨni amɨn gat, ae gɨptɨmni yokwi taŋbi amɨn gat, ae kandapmɨ yokwi taŋbi amɨn gat, ae dabɨlɨ mɨni amɨn gat yaŋ yobi.
Ji amɨn kɨnda dakon oman aŋek amɨn tagɨni dakon gen guramɨk kɨmotni.
Nak Piŋkop Yawe da gen yosok uŋun do mɨrak pakyaŋsi yopmaŋdat. Yokwi kalɨp agɨmaŋ uŋun ae dɨma aŋpakni yokwi aenin kɨneŋ kaŋ, uŋun da butnin paŋyawot aŋakwan tagɨsi egɨpneŋ do yosok.
Yaŋ kaŋek Yesu da abɨŋ kɨsirɨkon abɨdaŋek aban pɨdagɨt. Yaŋ aban sotni pasɨl ɨmɨŋakwan japni paŋnoman agɨt.
Yesu uŋudon da kɨŋ takis tɨmɨt tɨmɨt amɨn kɨnda kagɨt mani Liwai, uŋun takis tɨmɨt tɨmɨt yutnikon yɨkgɨt. Kaŋek yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Abɨŋ nak nol."
Do ji nandak nandakji yokwi kulabɨk aŋek but tobɨl ani, aŋakwa Piŋkop da dɨwarɨsi wɨrɨrɨk damjak.
Do nak jikon opbeŋ bɨsapmon mibɨlɨ nido asak uŋun dakon geni dayɨkeŋ. Uŋun gen yokwi mibɨlɨ mibɨlɨ yaŋ nimɨsak. Ae uŋun gɨn dɨma, not dɨwarɨ tɨmɨk paŋkɨ yutnikon dɨma paŋkɨsak. Ae amɨn dɨwarɨ paŋkɨ yop do aba uŋun kosiron baŋ kosiron da pabɨŋ yopmaŋ yomɨŋek paŋmuwukbi yolban waŋga abɨgɨŋ yolba kwaŋ.
Yoba tɨmɨk amɨn morap kɨsisi arɨpmɨsi naŋakwa jap dɨwat tawit uŋun paŋdetni da yɨk madepsi 7 yaŋ sɨmɨlba tugawit.
Jamba but amɨn uŋun namɨn? Amɨn kɨnda da Yesu uŋun Kristo dɨma yaŋ yosok uŋun Kristo. Yaŋ yosok amɨn uŋun Dat gat Monji gat manji yomɨsak, aŋek uŋun Kristo dakon uwalni asak.
Erot da Pita gen pikon aŋkɨ yɨpjak do bɨsap kɨnda yɨpgut. Uŋun bɨsapmon kalbi emat amɨn bamorɨ da dɨpmɨn pagakwan Pita nap teban bamorɨ baŋ paŋteban awit. Aŋakwa obip amɨn dɨwarɨ dam teban yut dakon yoma kagakon kɨla aŋek akgwit.
Amɨn morap kalugɨ egek nak nandaŋ gadaŋ namaŋ uŋun dɨma kɨmotdaŋ. Uŋun amɨn egɨp egɨp dagok dagogɨ mɨni egɨpdaŋ. Gak uŋun nandaŋ gadaŋ namɨsal bo dɨma?"
Gen Bin Tagɨsi uŋun Debe kokupmon yoyɨŋek amɨn morapmɨ paŋmuwukbi morapmɨsi awit. Yaŋ aŋek don Lista kokup pap ae Ikoniam ae Antiok kokup papmon tobɨl kɨgɨmal.
Nandani, amɨn morapmɨ nin paŋkewal do pi aŋ uŋun mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ akwaŋ. Uŋun amɨn Yesu Kristo uŋun amɨn dagaŋbi yaŋ dɨma nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmaŋ. Uŋuden amɨn uŋun top amɨn ae Kristo dakon uwalni.
Yawe da nin do nandaŋ yawok nimɨŋek yo tagɨsi aŋ nimɨsak. Piŋkopnin da nin do bupmɨ nandaŋ nimɨsak.
Aŋek uŋun da manon da mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ mɨŋat amɨn morap kabɨ kɨsikon Piŋkop dakon gen yoyɨŋ teŋteŋaŋ yomni. Yaŋ aŋek but tobɨl aŋakwa Piŋkop da dɨwarɨni wɨrɨrɨtjak. Pi madep uŋun Jerusalem da wasaŋek
Yesu Nasaret kokup yɨpmaŋek Kapaneam kokupmon paŋkɨ egɨpgut. Kapaneam kokup uŋun Galili Pakbi dap da ɨleŋɨkon tosok. Galili mɨktɨm uŋun Sebulan ae Naptali amɨn da mɨktɨmon tosok.
Yum pɨndagaki aŋpak yokwi da gak dɨma abɨŋ gepjak. Aŋpak tagɨ baŋ aŋek aŋpak yokwi pabɨŋ yopbi.
Piŋkop do pasolni, aŋek yokwi dɨma ani. Dɨpmɨn potpot tamokon pokgoŋ bɨsapmon uŋun do pakyaŋsi nandaŋek gen dɨma yaŋek tayaŋgok egɨpni.
Yaŋdo, nak nandak nandak on gam do abeŋ. Golno uŋun kɨndap da soŋek yo yokwi morapni wagɨl wɨrɨrɨk mudagɨt, do gak gol uŋun yum kaŋ tagɨsi, aŋaki moneŋ morapmɨ akdɨsal. Ae ɨmal kwakwagɨ baŋ gɨptɨmgo wɨtjɨki do yum kaŋ tagɨ. Yaŋ aŋaki amɨn da gak molaŋ molaŋ ae mayagɨsi egek dɨma gandani. Ae dabɨlgo sɨbɨt sɨbɨt dakon yo yum kaŋ, uŋun da tagɨ asak. Aŋek dabɨlgo dakon pakbi yum kaŋ, dabɨlgo sɨbɨt aŋakwan dabɨlgo sɨŋtjak.
Uŋun dɨmasi. Nin Piŋkop dakon nandaŋ kokwini tagɨsisi do gen yaŋ teŋteŋomaŋ. Piŋkop mɨktɨm dɨma wasagɨt bɨsapmon Piŋkop da nandak nandaknikon da nin iyɨ gat Kwen Kokupmon egɨpneŋ dakon kosit kɨlɨ manjɨgɨt. Mani uŋun dakon geni pasɨlɨ tagɨt.
Uŋudeŋ gɨn, Amɨn Tagɨ da gen yaŋ nimgut uŋun yaŋ: Gen Bin Tagɨsi yaŋ teŋteŋok aŋ amɨn uŋun gɨptɨm paŋpulugoni dakon yo tɨmɨkgaŋ.
"Amɨn da ji tɨmɨk paŋpaŋ muwut muwut yutnikon, ae gapman dakon amɨn madepmon, ae amɨn man madepni toŋ da ɨŋamon paŋkɨ depni bɨsapmon dɨma pasolni. 'Nin niaŋ gen baŋ paŋtobɨlneŋ? Bo ni gen baŋ yoyɨneŋ yaŋ do dɨma nandani.'
Oman monjɨ uŋun amɨn tagɨni da tobɨl abɨŋ kaŋban pini tagɨsi asak kaŋ tagɨsi.
Ae Piŋkop dakon papia da ae yaŋ yosok: "Amɨn Tagɨ da nandaŋ kokwini tagɨsi amɨn dakon nandak nandak kɨlɨ nandaŋ yomɨsak. Uŋun nandɨsak, yo morap ak do nandaŋ, uŋun bamɨ tagɨsi dɨma noman tokdaŋ."
Ji Kristo dakon gen yɨpba butjikon tebai tosak do bɨsit ani. Ji kaloŋ kaloŋ paŋmuwukbi dɨwarɨ yoyɨŋdet ani, aŋek nandak nandak tagɨsi gat ae nandak nandak tagɨsi gat yomni, aŋakwa aŋpak tagɨsi baŋgɨn ani. Aŋek butjikon da Piŋkop ya yaŋ iyɨŋek Kap Papia dakon kap, ae Piŋkop gawak ɨmɨm dakon kap, ae Telagɨ Wup da kap butjikon da paŋalon asak, uŋun kɨsi butjikon da kap yoni.
Piŋkop da bɨsap yɨpgut uŋun bɨsapmon yo morap abɨsok tasɨk togɨ dakon dam tebanon toŋ uŋun wɨrɨrɨkban pasɨldaŋ. Aŋakwan yo morap Piŋkop dakon mɨŋat monjɨyo nin gat tagɨsi egɨpneŋ.
Mani ji amɨn do nandaba yokwi tok madepsi aŋek bɨsapmɨ bɨsapmɨ dɨsi dakon man pawɨgɨk do kosit wusɨk aŋ kaŋ, nandak nandakji tagɨsi gat ae nandaŋ kokwinji tagɨsi gat do kɨsɨk kɨsɨk dɨma ani. Ji topmon da gen bamɨ dɨ abɨŋ yɨpmaŋbam.
Amɨn kɨnda gen on papiakon mandaŋ damamaŋ uŋun dɨma guramɨtjak kaŋ, uŋun amɨn ji da dubagɨkon egek mayagɨ pak do bɨkbɨk ɨmni.
Nandak nandakgo da nak yapmaŋdak, nandak nandakno yapmaŋdak.
Ji kɨlɨ kɨlek tawit. Gen dayɨsat uŋun da ji paŋmɨlɨp asak.
Telagɨ Wup da kɨlɨ iyɨgɨt, uŋun tepmɨ dɨma kɨmotjak. Mibɨltok Amɨn Tagɨ da Kristo yabekban abɨŋ kokdɨsak.
Ji Piŋkop do pasalek pasal ɨmni. Mɨktɨmon gawak ɨmɨŋek kɨsɨk kɨsɨk aŋek egɨpni.
Pita da uŋun amɨn kaŋek Yesu yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Amɨn Tagɨ, uŋun amɨn niaŋ agagɨ?"
Pega kokupmon Piŋkop gen yoyɨŋek don Atalia kokup papmon pɨgɨgɨmal.
Ae samɨni mɨŋat morap nin gat ekwamaŋ. Uŋun da niaŋon da yo uŋun asak?"
Yaŋ yaŋba Pilip da Nataniel kɨŋ kaŋ wɨsɨŋ kaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Amɨn kɨnda kalɨp Moses da gen teban papiakon mandagɨt, ae kombɨ amɨn kɨsi da gen mandawit uŋun kɨlɨ mandawit. Uŋun amɨn mani Yesu, Josep dakon monji, Nasaret kokupmon nani. Uŋun kɨlɨ mandawit."
Kalɨpsigwan Piŋkop da yaŋ yagɨt, "Pɨlɨn tukgwan da teŋteŋɨ noman tosak." Yaŋ yaŋakwan Piŋkop dakon teŋteŋɨni da abɨŋ ninon yɨpban teŋteŋagɨt. Aŋek Yesu Kristo da tomno dabɨlon teŋteŋɨ bamɨsi kagɨmaŋ. Aŋek Piŋkop dakon teŋteŋɨ madepni uŋun kaŋ nandaŋyo agɨmaŋ.
Kabap morapmon sɨŋtaŋ egɨsat. Mani yokwikon baŋ pulugaŋ nepjak amɨn dukwan da apjak?
Do Juda amɨn gat egɨpgumaŋ bɨsapmon Juda amɨn dakon aŋpak yolek Juda amɨn tɨmɨt do aŋek egɨpgum. Naga Moses dakon gen teban da yoŋgamgwan dɨma egɨsat, mani mɨŋat amɨnyo gen teban da yoŋgamgwan ekwaŋ amɨn tɨmɨt do aŋek uŋun da dabɨlon gen teban da yoŋgamgwan egɨsat.
Kaŋek yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Nandaki, gak uŋun do amɨn dɨma yoyɨŋek kɨŋ mukwa sogogon gɨptɨmgo yolɨki. Aŋek Moses da yagɨt uŋun da tɨlagon paret aŋaki amɨn da asi kɨlek tal yaŋ gandani."
Yesu da saŋbeŋek yaŋ yagɨt, "Ji pik kɨndap kaŋek butji pɨsosak. Kɨlɨŋɨ pakbini toŋ ae tamɨ kaluk yopmaŋdak, uŋun bɨsapmon gɨldat bɨsap kwaŋ tosok yaŋ nandaŋ.
Yesu da yo agɨt uŋun kaŋek Juda amɨn morapmɨ Maria dakon but paŋpulugok do apgwit uŋun da kaŋek nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmgwit.
Datno da mɨŋat amɨnyo namgut uŋun da yo morap kɨsi yapmaŋ mudosok, do amɨn kɨnda da arɨpmɨ dɨma paŋabɨŋ kɨsiron baŋ arɨpmɨ dɨma paŋkɨsak.
Yesu da uŋun amɨn kaŋek gen teban yoyɨŋdet amɨn gat ae Parisi amɨn gat yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Sabat bɨsapmon amɨn kɨnda da notni kɨnda aŋmɨlɨp asak kaŋ, uŋun gen teban yapmaŋgaŋ bo dɨma?"
Jap do agɨm bɨsapmon pakbi emarɨ toŋ namɨŋ, ae pakbi do tekno bap taŋakwan wain ɨsalɨ naba nosot.
Monjɨno Timoti, nak kombɨ amɨn da kalɨp gak do gen yawit uŋun do nandaŋek yo abi do gen on gamgum. Kombɨ amɨn da gen uŋun gayɨŋba uŋun da aŋpak yokwi pabɨŋ yop do tapmɨm gamɨŋakwan emat tebaisi abi.
Mani ji amɨn dakon yokwini dɨma yopmaŋ yomni kaŋ, Datji da yokwisi dɨma yopmaŋ damjak."
Yawe uŋun kɨla amɨn madep egɨsak. Mɨktɨm ji kɨsɨk kɨsɨk ani. Ae tap binap mɨktɨm tɨm toŋ mɨktɨm toŋ ji but galak nandaŋek kɨsɨk kɨsɨk ani.
Amɨn da joŋ bamaŋba kɨbɨdoŋ uŋun da tɨlak Piŋkop da abɨŋ nepgut, do jap do saŋbeŋek dɨma galak tosot.
Yaŋ yaŋek yutnon wɨgɨgɨmal mani Amɨn Tagɨ Yesu dakon bumjotni dɨma kawit.
Bɨsapmɨ bɨsapmɨ pi tebaisi aŋek Telagɨ Wup da paŋtagap aban Amɨn Tagɨ dakon pi ani.
Nin Yawe do pasal ɨmneŋ. Uŋun Piŋkop Wukwisi. Uŋun Kɨla Amɨn Madep Wukwisi egek mɨktɨmon mɨŋat amɨn morap kɨsi kɨla asak.
Aŋakwa amɨn uŋun waseŋ kɨŋ mɨktɨm morap kɨŋek Gen Bin Tagɨsi yoyɨŋ teŋteŋaŋ yomgwit.
Yaŋ kaŋakwan Yesu da iyɨgɨt, "Mɨŋat gak kunam nido takdal? Namɨn amɨn naŋ wɨsaŋ?" Maria uŋun wain pi dakon kɨla amɨn yaŋ nandaŋek yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Amɨn tagɨ, abɨdaŋ aŋkɨlɨgɨl kaŋ, dukwan yɨpgul uŋudon nayɨŋbɨ kaŋbɨ abɨdaŋ aŋkɨkeŋ."
Mani mɨŋat gɨmoŋɨ sakwabat dakon man dɨma mandaki. Nido, but tobɨl pak do galagɨ nandaŋ bɨsapmon Kristo manji ɨmaŋ,
Yaŋ yaŋek mɨrɨmni pɨsoŋakwan pɨŋ yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Telagɨ Wup abɨdoni.
Yawe da amɨn kɨlegɨ kɨlani aŋek bɨsitni nandaŋ yomɨsak.
Yawe, uwalno gat emat wamaŋek pabɨŋ yopbi. Emat agak sɨbago abɨdaŋek uwalno gat emat wamɨŋek yokwi pakpak da kɨsiron baŋ pulugaŋ nepbi.
Yo morap uŋun altaŋakwa Piŋkop da ji yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨtjak bɨsap kɨlɨ uŋun kwaŋ tosok, do ji tebai agek busuŋji paŋenagek atni."
Yawe da dɨpmɨn dɨma pokdot. Butno jɨk tosok, do gen arɨpmɨ dɨma yokeŋ.
Amɨn morap amɨn do nandaŋ yawot aŋ yomaŋ amɨn, uŋun Piŋkop da nandaŋ yawot aŋ yomdɨsak, do uŋun kɨsɨk kɨsɨk ekwaŋ.
Yaŋ yaŋbal yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Jil kokup papmon kɨŋ kaŋbal amɨn kɨnda pakbi kwoba kɨnda guramɨk apban jil gat domdom akdaŋ. Jil uŋun amɨn yol aŋkɨ yutnon wɨgɨsak.
Oman amɨngo nak gen pikon dɨma nepbi. Nido, amɨn kɨlegɨ kɨlegɨ kɨnda gak da dabɨlon dɨma egɨsak.
Mani amɨn kɨnda aŋpak bamɨsi asak uŋun amɨn Piŋkop da tapmɨmon da pi asak yaŋ kaŋ nandaŋyo ani do teŋteŋɨkon apɨsak."
Yaŋban amɨn kɨsi da yaŋ iyɨwit, "Gulusuŋnin nin gat ae mɨŋat monjɨyonin gat kɨsi da tɨmɨtneŋ."
Uŋun bɨsapmon gen teban dakon mibɨlɨ nandak nandak amɨn kɨnda da abɨŋ Yesu yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Yoyɨŋdet, dukwan dukwan agɨpbi uŋun nak gol awɨlgeŋ gɨn."
Pol uŋun kokup pap yɨpmaŋek Debe ae Lista kokup pap kɨsi kɨŋ altagɨt. Uŋun kokup papmon Yesu nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmgut amɨn kɨnda egɨpgut mani Timoti. Timoti uŋun Juda mɨŋat kɨnda Yesu nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmgut. Mani datni uŋun Grik amɨn kɨnda.
Uŋun da gen pap yaŋ tɨdaŋek gen yokwi yaŋ namaŋek yaŋ yoŋ, "Asisi, aŋpak yokwisi asal."
Nin Kristo nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmɨŋek yo tagɨsi aŋ nimjak do jomjom amaŋ. Mani on mɨktɨm dakon egɨp egɨp dakon yo dogɨn nandaŋ teban taŋek jomjom amaŋ kaŋ, nin on mɨktɨm dakon amɨn dɨwarɨ yapmaŋgamaŋ.
Niaŋ? Paŋmuwukbikon dɨma saŋbeŋbi amɨn dakon aŋpak kokwin ak do pi asat uŋun ji da agagɨ. Dɨmasi! Mani paŋmuwukbikon ekwaŋ amɨn dakon aŋpak kokwin ak do pi ji da agagɨ.
Aŋek kabap morap ae tɨp morapmon pɨdaŋek yaŋ tɨdaŋek yaŋ yawit, "Ji nin wɨtjɨŋba pasɨlneŋ. Aŋek Amɨn uŋun kɨla amɨn madep yɨtyɨt tamonikon yɨkdak uŋun da ɨŋamon pasɨlni. Aŋakwa Sipsip Monɨŋ da butjapni madepsi gat abɨŋek yo yokwisi dɨma aŋnimjak.
Yaŋ iyɨ dakon tomno dabɨl pɨndakgɨt, mani kɨŋek uŋudon gɨn niaŋen amɨn kɨnda yaŋ uŋun do ɨŋtaŋek kɨgɨt.
mal dubakni kon ae kandap mibɨlɨkon man yaŋ mandawit, Kɨla Amɨn Madep morap dakon Kɨla Amɨn Madepni ae Amɨn Tagɨ morap dakon Amɨn Tagɨni.
Yaŋ aba ji nak nolgaŋ do aŋek amɨn kɨsi morap da ji do butjap nandakdaŋ. Mani tebai agek egɨ wɨgakwa bɨsap madepmon wɨgɨsak amɨn uŋun Piŋkop da yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨtdɨsak.
Uwalno morapmɨ, do kunam tagek iyoŋ iyoŋ yaŋek egɨsat. Dabɨlno pɨrɨropmaŋdak. Yo kɨnda arɨpmɨ dɨma kosot.
Dewit uŋun Yesu Kwen Kokup wɨgɨgɨt uŋudeŋ dɨma wɨgɨgɨt. Mani Dewit da yaŋ yagɨt: 'Amɨn Tagɨ da nak dakon Amɨn Tagɨno yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Gak abɨŋ nak da amɨnsi tet do yɨkbɨ
Piŋkop Datnin gat ae Amɨn Tagɨ Yesu Kristo gat da nandaŋ yawok damɨŋek butji paŋyawot abal yaworɨ tosak do bɨsit amak.
Yesu da saŋbeŋek yaŋ yagɨt, "Yo jɨgɨ dakon bɨsap mudaŋakwan, uŋun bɨsapmon gɨldat dabɨl pɨlɨn tuk akdɨsak, ae kanek dɨma teŋteŋaŋ mudokdɨsak.
Piŋkop uŋun amɨn da arɨpmɨ dɨma kokogɨ, mani Monji uŋun Piŋkop yombemsi. Uŋun Piŋkop dakon Monji mibɨltogɨ, ae yo morap Piŋkop da wasagɨt uŋun dakon busuŋɨ wukwisi egɨsak.
Kalɨp Piŋkop da yaŋ yagɨt: "Aisagon da babɨkgo altokdaŋ, uŋun do aŋek Abraham dakon yawi da altawit yaŋ dɨma yomaŋ."
Ae mɨktɨm kalugɨ Piŋkop da don aŋkaluk akdɨsak uŋun do nandamaŋ kaŋ, nin nandamaŋ, Piŋkop da aŋelo kabɨ baŋ dɨma kɨlani ani do yopgut.
Yaŋba Yesu da yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Nak da paŋdetno 12 kabɨ ji manjɨgɨm, mani jikon da kɨnda koŋ kɨnda asak."
Gen yaŋakwan uwalni da mayaktok madepsi pawit. Aŋakwan mɨŋat amɨn morapyo da wasok tapmɨmɨ toŋ morap agɨt uŋun do kɨsɨk kɨsɨk awit.
Piŋkop da ɨleŋ dubagɨsi kɨndakon wɨgɨgɨt da amɨn morapmɨ iyɨ teban taŋek tɨmɨkgɨt uŋun kɨsi tɨmɨkban kɨwit. Iyɨ do nandaba wɨgɨsak amɨn da uwal aŋ ɨmgwit uŋun dakon but galak dakon yo tɨmɨkgɨt. Piŋkop Yawe uŋun kabapmon egɨpdɨsak.
Amɨn Tagɨnin Yesu Kristo dakon nandaŋ yawotni ji kɨsikon tosak do bɨsit amaŋ.
Nak ji Amɨn Tagɨ do nandaŋek Pibi abɨdaŋba ji gat kɨsi egɨpjak do nandɨsat. Pibi dakon mɨŋat amɨnyo da yaŋ gɨn ani kaŋ, ji da aŋpulugoni do nandɨsat. Nido, uŋun da amɨn morapmɨsi paŋpulugagɨt, ae nakyo kɨsi yaŋ gɨn paŋpulugagɨt.
Yaŋ iyɨŋban oman monjɨni da kokup pap da kosit madepmon agek amɨn pɨndakgwit uŋun paŋmuwuk yopba yɨgek jap noknok tamokon yɨgek tugawit.
Not kabɨ, nin ji gat egek Gen Bin Tagɨsi yaŋ teŋteŋagɨmaŋ bɨsapmon pi madepsi agɨmaŋ uŋun dɨsi nandaŋ. Nin ji gat egek japnin paŋpulugok do jɨgɨ dɨma damneŋ yaŋ do gɨldarɨ ae kalbi pi tebaisi agɨmaŋ.
Ji ŋugɨgɨsi kɨlɨ dagawit, ma? Ji Telagɨ Wup da tapmɨmon wasaŋek egɨpgwit, abɨsok dɨsi da tapmɨmon wasɨp ak do nandaŋ, ma?
Mani Pita da Saimon yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Moneŋgo gat gaga gat kɨsi tasɨk tosak! Piŋkop da but galak do yo nimɨsak uŋun moneŋ baŋ tagɨ yumneŋ yaŋ nandɨsal, ma? Uŋun dɨmasi!
Uŋun da kwenon aeno kaŋapbo Piŋkop dakon Telagɨ Yut Madepni Kwen Kokupmon wɨtdal kɨgɨt. Uŋun Piŋkop geni bamɨ aŋteban asak.
Dɨsi nandaŋ, kalɨp ji koron olip kɨndap kɨlɨŋ egɨpgwit, aŋakwa Piŋkop da ji mandaŋ dagaŋban olip kɨndap tagɨsikon saŋbekeŋ. Uŋun ji dakon kɨndap dɨma, do olip kɨndap da kɨlɨŋɨ uŋudon paŋtobɨl paŋtobɨlban kɨŋ kɨndasok dɨma akdaŋ.
"Nak on mɨktɨmon mɨŋat amɨnyo da tɨlɨmgo ae tapmɨmgo yolɨgɨm. Pi abeŋ do namgul uŋun kɨlɨ aŋ mudosot.
Do yaŋ gayɨsat, on mɨŋat da nak do but dasi galak taŋ namɨsak. Piŋkop da dɨwarɨni morapmɨ yopmaŋ ɨmɨŋ ɨmgut, mani amɨn kɨnda yokwi kaloŋɨsok dɨ gat aŋakwan Piŋkop da dɨwarɨni wɨrɨrɨk ɨmjak kaŋ, uŋun amɨn galaktokni kaloŋɨsok dɨ dɨma nandɨsak."
Nido mɨktɨmnikon kɨmagek pasol pasolɨ mɨni Amɨn Tagɨnin Yesu Kristo dakon man yaŋ teŋteŋok agɨmal.
Yaŋba yaŋ yoyɨgɨt, "Nak gen kɨnda dayɨkdɨsat uŋun dayɨko nayɨni.
Nin Piŋkop dakon uwalni egɨpgumaŋ bɨsapmon Monji da uwal uŋun paŋupbal aŋek nin Piŋkop gat but kaloŋ ano kɨmakgɨt. Abɨsok Monji da egɨp egɨp dagok dagogɨ mɨni abɨdagɨt, do nin Piŋkop gat but kaloŋ ekwamaŋ amɨn da yaŋsi nandamaŋ, Monji uŋun da egɨp egɨpnikon da Piŋkop da nin yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨtdɨsak yaŋsi nandaneŋ.
Uŋun kaloŋ gɨn tɨp madepno ae yokwikon baŋ tɨmɨt tɨmɨt amɨno. Uŋun kaloŋgɨn dam tebano arɨpmɨ dɨma tuwɨlɨ, do uwalno da arɨpmɨ dɨma abɨŋ nepni.
Kabap madep da meme da yaŋ wɨgɨ mokmok awit, ae ɨleŋ monɨŋ monɨŋ da sipsip da yaŋ wɨgɨ mokmok awit.
Yaŋdo, kɨla amɨnji da nak gat kɨsi pɨgɨni. Pɨgakwa on amɨn gulusuŋ kɨnda agɨt kaŋ, gen pikon yɨpni."
Yaŋban Pita da iyɨgɨt, "Nayɨŋbɨ nandako, mɨktɨm dakon moneŋ bamot uŋun baŋ moneŋ tɨmɨkgamal, ma?" Yaŋban mɨŋat da yaŋ iyɨgɨt, "Uŋun asi."
Mani Yawe, nak gak do nandaŋ gadasat. Nak yaŋ yosot, gak Piŋkopno.
Piŋkop dakon mɨŋat amɨnyo paŋmuwukbi da but kaloŋon da egɨpni kaŋ, uŋun tagɨsi ae tagɨsi asak. Uŋun da tagɨsi aŋek butni tagɨsi tosak.
Israel amɨn kabɨ, egɨp egɨpji Yawekon tosok yaŋsi nandani. Abɨsok ae don kɨsi taŋ aŋaŋ kɨkdɨsak.
Yawe, gak Piŋkop Wukwisi. Gak mɨktɨm morap kɨsi kɨla asal. Kɨla amɨn madep dakon man madepgo da piŋkop toptopmɨ morap yapmaŋ mudosok.
Yawe da don oman amɨni Moses gat Aron gat manjɨŋek yabekban Isip kɨwit.
Yawe da nin do aŋpak tagɨsi aŋ nimɨsak. Dɨsi aŋkɨlɨk nandaŋek Yawe uŋun tagɨsi yaŋ kɨlɨ kaŋ nandaŋyo ani. Amɨn morap egɨp egɨpni Yawekon tosok yaŋsi nandaŋ amɨn uŋun but galaksi nandani.
Uŋun bɨsapmon Telagɨ Wup da Yesu do kɨsɨk kɨsɨk madepsi aŋ ɨban yaŋ yagɨt, "Dat, kundu ae mɨktɨm dakon Amɨn Tagɨ, amɨn nandaŋ kokwini tagɨsi, ae nandaŋ kokwini tagɨsi, uŋun amɨnon yo morap si paŋkɨsɨbɨgɨl, aŋek amɨn monɨŋɨ da tɨlagon ekwaŋ amɨn do yolɨsal. Asi, Dat, gak gaga dakon galaktok yolek yaŋ asal."
Yaŋ yaŋban kɨla amɨn Pol da gen uŋun yaŋban nandaŋek Piŋkop aŋkɨsiŋek yaŋ iyɨwit, "Not, gaga nandɨsal, Juda amɨn tausen morapmɨ da Yesu nandaŋ gadaŋ ɨmgwit. Ae Juda amɨn kabɨ morapmɨ da Moses dakon gen teban guramɨt do galagɨsi nandaŋ.
Bɨsapmɨ bɨsapmɨ kɨsɨk kɨsɨk aŋek egɨpni. Ae aeno yosot, kɨsɨk kɨsɨk aŋek egɨpni.
Yesu gen uŋun yoyɨŋ mudaŋek Galili Provins yɨpmaŋek Judia Provinskon Jodan Pakbi usugap tet do kɨgɨt.
Piŋkop uŋun kɨla amɨn madep egek mɨŋat amɨn morap kɨsi kɨla asak. Piŋkop kɨla amɨn madep yɨtyɨt tamonikon yɨkdak, aŋpakni uŋun kɨlegɨsi.
